Package uml_parser.collectors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregationCollector
    This class collects an Aggregation which correspond to 'AGGREGATION' 'CONTAINER' 'PARTS' ; (with/without spaces).
    AssociationCollector
    This class collects an Association which correspond to 'RELATION''ROLES',; (with/without spaces).
    ClassContentCollector
    This class collects an Operation which correspond to (): (with/without spaces).
    DataitemCollector
    This class collects a Dataitem which correspond to : (with/without spaces).
    DataitemListCollector
    This class collects a DataitemList which correspond to [{,}] (with/without spaces).
    GeneralizationCollector
    This class collects a Generalization which correspond to 'GENERALIZATION''SUBCLASSES'; (with/without spaces).
    IdentifierListCollector
    This class collects a list of identifiers which correspond to [{,}] (with/without spaces).
    ModelCollector
    This class collects a mix of ClassContentCollector, AssociationCollector, GeneralizationCollector and AggregationCollector declarations and use them to represent a UML schema.
    OperationCollector
    This class collects an Operation which correspond to (): (with/without spaces).
    OperationListCollector
    This class collects a Dataitem which correspond to : (with/without spaces).
    RoleCollector
    This class collects a Dataitem which correspond to : (with/without spaces).
    RoleListCollector
    This class collects a RoleList which correspond to {,} (with/without spaces).
